                        <item xml:id="e8"><desc> - Cues for the rubricator: e.g., <locus target="#31v">31v</locus>, 32r, 36v, 38v, 53v, 62r. </desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e9"><desc> - Crude drawing in pencil
                           on <locus target="#1v">1v</locus> and crude notes in pen on <locus target="#39r">39r</locus> and 87v. </desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e10"><desc> - Personal names, i.e. Gabra Hiwet and Gabra Mikāʾel, are crudely written on <locus target="#87v">87v</locus> (bottom margin).</desc></item>
